 building things."}]}]},{"type":"element","name":"section","elements":[{"type":"element","name":"rac_column_heds_with_rule","elements":[{"type":"text","text":"Connect the Texts"}]},{"type":"element","name":"rac_teacher-talk_blue","elements":[{"type":"element","name":"rac_teacher-talk_emphasis_non-ital","elements":[{"type":"text","text":"Bird Builds a Nest "}]},{"type":"text","text":"is about a Bird building a nest with twigs and feathers. "},{"type":"element","name":"rac_teacher-talk_emphasis_non-ital","elements":[{"type":"text","text":"The Three Little Rabbits "}]},{"type":"text","text":"is about rabbits building houses with straw, sticks, and bricks. Let’s see what we can learn about building a strong house!"}]},{"type":"element","name":"rac_hilight_teacher_inst_new","elements":[{"type":"text","text":"Show the "},{"type":"element","name":"rac_highlight_teacher_inst_Italic","elements":[{"type":"text","text":"Bird Builds a Nest"}]},{"type":"text","text":" cover."}]}]},{"type":"element","name":"section","elements":[{"type":"element","name":"rac_column_heds_with_rule","elements":[{"type":"text","text":"Revisit the Concept Question"}]},{"type":"element","name":"rac_teacher-talk_blue","elements":[{"type":"text","text":"How do we build things?"}]}]},{"type":"element","name":"section","elements":[{"type":"element","name":"rac_column_heds_with_rule","elements":[{"type":"text","text":"Close-Read: Connect to Building"}]},{"type":"element","name":"rac_body-text","elements":[{"type":"text","text":"Read aloud the teacher text on the Big Chart stopping to ask questions. Use Equity Sticks to choose children to respond."}]},{"type":"element","name":"rac_d-hed_page_number","elements":[{"type":"text","text":"He made a house of straw."}]},{"type":"element","name":"rac_teacher-talk_blue","elements":[{"type":"text","text":"What did Ryan Rabbit use to build his house? Do you think straw is heavy or light? "}]},{"type":"element","name":"rac_hilight_teacher_inst_new","elements":[{"type":"